---
description: Centralize temporary debug instrumentation
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

# Debug Instrumentation

- Do not scatter raw `fetch(...)` debug snippets across feature, route, or realtime files.
- Put debug transport details in one helper and call that helper from the instrumented code.
- Keep instrumentation compact: each call should pass `hypothesisId`, `location`, `message`, and safe structured `data`.
- Do not log secrets, tokens, credentials, or personally identifiable data.
